{"tid":2287483,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國法院裁定沃爾夫署任國土安全部長不合法","createTime":"2020-11-15T20:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T05:41:54.000Z","uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"67ed28f6c1826c44dd01622b0e3dd9faa780feb2","tid":2287483,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T20:21:08.000Z","msg":"美國紐約的聯邦地區法院裁定，沃爾夫署任國土安全部長並非合法任命，他暫停「追夢者計劃」的決定亦不合法。<br />\n<br />\n裁決指，前任部長尼爾森辭職後，中間署任的人、海關及邊境保衛局專員麥卡利南，並非合法繼任，因為按規定應由部門內的網絡安全與基礎設施安全局主管接任，以致再之後繼任的沃爾夫，也並非合法任命，所以沃爾夫也無權行使國土安全部長的權力，因此他任內發出關於暫停「追夢者計劃」的備忘並沒有效力，裁決即變相恢復容許未成年非法移民暫時留在美國，等候申請居留結果的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sFnQsIYkfxM&amp;ab_channel=%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96CABLETV%26%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9ECABLENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsFnQsIYkfxM%26ab_channel%3D%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596CABLETV%2526%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259ECABLENews&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3j11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=083f7f42\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sFnQsIYkfxM&amp;ab_channel=%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96CABLETV%26%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9ECABLENews</a>"},{"pid":"53de8938b7b6d5f0f296bd34ce44f9831d4412ad","tid":2287483,"uid":261913,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T20:23:47.000Z","msg":"紐約南區聯邦地區法院<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475a52bdf141aba8fae3399bc68a2d1ba6c94bd2","tid":2287483,"uid":154486,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T20:26:27.000Z","msg":"Supreme Court<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73292739f38efe5d4e0d40714b7355cf0ff9b68","tid":2287483,"uid":121146,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T02:41:31.000Z","msg":"E個理由幾搞笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\